'''''Chuvappu Naada''''' is a [[Malayalam films of 1990|1990]] [[Cinema of India|Indian]] [[Malayalam language|Malayalam]] film, directed by [[K. S. Gopalakrishnan]]. The film has musical score by [[S. P. Venkatesh]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.malayalachalachithram.com/movie.php?i=2341|title=Chuvappunaada|accessdate=2014-10-14|publisher=www.malayalachalachithram.com}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://malayalasangeetham.info/m.php?3195|title=Chuvappunaada|accessdate=2014-10-14|publisher=malayalasangeetham.info}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://spicyonion.com/title/chuvappu-naada-malayalam-movie/|title=Chuvappu Naada|accessdate=2014-10-14|publisher=spicyonion.com}}</ref>
==Cast== {{<ref>Noor Nisha</ref> }}
==Soundtrack== The music was composed by [[S. P. Venkatesh]] and the lyrics were written by [[Poovachal Khader]] and [[Bharanikkavu Sivakumar]].
